<title>USA: TABLE- Sterling Software Q3 oper net rises.</title>
<headline>TABLE- Sterling Software Q3 oper net rises.</headline>
<dateline>DALLAS 1997-08-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>1997			1996</p>
<p> Shr oper profit	  $0.48   profit	 $0.47</p>
<p> Shr loss		    4.81   profit	  0.80</p>
<p> Net oper profit	 27,478   profit	24,990</p>
<p> Net loss		 185,463   profit	17,358</p>
<p> Revs		     114,244		  110,546</p>
<p> Avg shrs		  38,533		   35,758</p>
<p>	  NINE MONTHS</p>
<p> Shr oper profit	  $1.19   profit	 $1.16</p>
<p> Shr loss		    4.09   profit	  5.80</p>
<p> Net oper profit	 70,474   profit	54,538</p>
